<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.8.11">
<l>kaṇṭalaṅkaḷ ceyya karumēṉi yammāṉai</l>
<l>vaṇṭalampuñ cōlai vaḻuti vaḷanāṭaṉ</l>
<l>paṇṭalaiyil coṉṉatami ḻāyirattip pattumvallār</l>
<l>viṇṭalaiyil vīṟṟirun tāḷvarem māvīṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these ten in the Tamil thousand spoken within the range of the melodies</l>
<l>by the man from the prosperous land of Vaḻuti with groves where bees hum</l>
<l>on the lord with a black body red in the eye area</l>
<l>will sit in distinction in the area of heaven [and] rule our great liberation.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
